@startuml
hide footbox
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantPadding 30
  BoxPadding 10
}

actor User
participant DisplayFragment
participant ReportFragment
participant Report
participant Firebase
participant ReportedFragment

User -> DisplayFragment : Click plus button
DisplayFragment -> ReportFragment
User -> ReportFragment : Press a category button
ReportFragment -> Report
ReportFragment -> Firebase : Report
ReportFragment -> ReportedFragment
User -> ReportedFragment : Press "Return to Map" button

@enduml